title: Broken Heart Blvd
description:
I never thought,
It'd be this hard,
Just walking down,
Broken Heart Blvd,
Didn't want to feel,
All this pain,
But today got stuck,
On Memory Lane,
Hoped I'd see you,
At I miss You Park,
But once again,
Alone in the dark,
Wish you'd come,
To Apology Circle,
Then I'd say,
I'm sorry I hurt you,
Just know I'm heading,
To Recovery Road,
Wishing you were here,
To Love and hold,
Integrity Avenue,
Is under construction,
Finally repairing,
My self destruction,
Without you,
I'm so incomplete,
Hope i find you on,
I still Love You Street!

Joshua Jones

04-27-2011
